        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6848",
        "content": "And although mr Lake was a man of vast activities and complicated engagements he was coming now to Europe for the express purpose of seeing v v and having things out with her fully and completely because, in spite of all that had happened, she made such an endless series of delays in coming to America.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
