        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6848",
        "content": "At the thought of a lover for v v a sudden flood of anger poured across the old man's mind, behind the still mask of his face.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
