        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6848",
        "content": "It infuriated him even to think of v v, his little v v, his own girl, entertaining a lover, being possibly-most shameful thought-IN LOVE!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
