        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6848",
        "content": "It would be pleasant to go about with her on his right hand in Paris, HIS girl, straight and lovely, desirable and unapproachable,--above that sort of nonsense, above all other masculine subjugation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
